column1: #Text=This week I think Australia has a pretty good , strong team from a standing perspective , so we 're probably racing against each other .
#Text=So you do not care about the Chileans , or whoever , hanging around ?
#Text=The Canadian and American teams are here , and they 've got some developing athletes .
#Text=Probably more the Europeans who are developing who 've got the highest others skiing in our particular division , and the Americans are very strong with their sit skiers .

#Text=So this week being just a North American -based race we 'll probably be looking at the other two in terms of racing , but yeah , when we get over to the world cups over in Europe in January , that 's when the whole field 's together , and gives us some idea of what we 're racing against .
#Text=I feel like we 're almost coming to a close .
#Text=What do you do outside of skiing ?
#Text=I work as a physiotherapist , and I am a family man .
#Text=Since Vancouver I have n't skied a huge amount since then .
#Text=I 've got a little boy , and so other priorities definitely start to take effect .
#Text=I think as a skier , it 's a challenge from the travelling perspective when you do have family .
#Text=I think that 's unlike a lot of summer athletes who have their training base next door .
#Text=For us , we need to be always on the move , so that 's always one of the challenges with alpine skiing .
#Text=You get the privilege of travelling but you 're away from your family , so for me , my last year I have focused more on family life and sort of getting back into the skiing this year .
#Text=I 'm a bit younger than these guys so I 'm ...
#Text=So I 've got pretty much a year to go now , but that 'll take me two years to do just because of where Sochi is , in March 2014

#Text=I 'll cut back this year coming , 2013 , and I 'll only do probably about half — I 'll do five subjects as opposed to eight , just because when you 're out travelling during the year and prepping , using your weekend to ski will it getting to you like that .
#Text=With the schedule , from June to the end September will be pretty much flat skiing .
#Text=Last time I did that leading into Vancouver , I mean I do that every year but probably a bigger load in the games lead that kind of thing .
#Text=And I did that in the middle of Year 12 last time , and that was interesting , but now I can actually ...
